Option A is incorrect because it places the page number before the text, resulting in "X Type 1 Page".

Option C is incorrect because it uses the plain page style instead of fancy, which won't allow for custom headers and footers.

Option D is incorrect because it places the custom page number in the right footer (rfoot) instead of the center footer (cfoot) as specified in the question.

